title: Pumpkin cake
ingredients: ['250g plain flour', '3 teaspoons baking powder', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoons salt', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '400g caster sugar', '250ml vegetable oil', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '500g tinned pumpkin puree', '4 eggs', '125g chopped walnuts (optional)']
